```

## Development

To set up the development environment:

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/promptons.git
cd promptons

# Install poetry if you haven't already
pip install poetry

# Install dependencies
poetry install

# Run tests
poetry run pytest
```

